      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/113892.Charles_R_Johnson">About Charles R. Johnson</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/113892.Charles_R_Johnson"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1380235439p3/113892.jpg);'></div>
